Fonts
=====

Here are the fonts that I use. Some are more suited for laptop, other for
desktop. Some fonts look better in console, others in emacs.

Manual installation
-------------------

ttf-mscorefonts-installer
fonts-inconsolata
fonts-lmodern

# Fix for ttf-mscorefonts-installer when problems arise
sudo dpkg -P ttf-mscorefonts-installer
sudo rm -rf /var/lib/update-notifier/package-data-downloads/partial/*
sudo apt-get --purge --reinstall install ttf-mscorefonts-installer

# Installing Windows Vista fonts (Consolas)
wget http://plasmasturm.org/code/vistafonts-installer/vistafonts-installer
bash vistafonts-installer

Automatic installation
----------------------

hermit
source-code-pro
